    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While the engine starts, it suffers from significant oil leaks and a rough idle that suggests a need for immediate mechanical attention. The transmission is also showing signs of wear with delayed engagement and slipping between gears. Externally, the car has several large dents and noticeable rust bubbling on the wheel arches, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a source for parts, but it is not currently reliable for daily transportation.",
