      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard used market. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, this unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that is indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who demands peak performance and aesthetic perfection without compromise.",
