    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single enthusiast owner, resulting in a flawless exterior finish with a deep, mirror-like luster and absolutely zero imperfections. Step inside to find an interior that remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear, the dashboard is pristine, and it still retains that distinctive new-car scent. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule. Every button, switch, and feature operates with precision. With exceptionally low mileage and a level of care that borders on obsessive, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example. This isn't just a used car; it is a time capsule preserved for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to the highest standards of excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original state. A rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
