    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! I've taken such good care of this car that it's still in absolutely flawless, showroom condition. It drives like an absolute dream and looks brand new inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. It's been my pride and joy, and it's ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
