    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement with treated shells. The subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing is tight, the cooling system is refreshed, and the paint depth is consistent across all panels. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
